    cat file.txt | grep "error"

    âœ… RHCA Tip: While cat is simple, RHCA expects you to know when to avoid unnecessary usage. Example: cat file | grep something is better written as grep something file.

âš ï¸ Best Practices & Misuse

    âœ… Good: cat file.txt

    âŒ Bad: cat file.txt | less â†’ better: less file.txt

